I"<p>Marat is heavily inspired by <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%27Ami_du_peuple">Lâ€™Ami du peuple</a>, a newspaper written by <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean-Paul_Marat">Jean-Paul Marat</a> during the French Revolution, and thus may not be used to promote any form of totalitarianism and should rather be used to advance democracy and revive the Age of Reason.</p>

<p>Marat is fully responsive, light and fast.</p>

<ol>
  <li>Adapt the _config.yml file</li>
  <li>Replace/Delete the posts</li>
  <li>Change this page: about.md</li>
  <li>Change or add your links in the nav.yml file located in the _data folder</li>
  <li>Replace favicon.ico in root folder</li>
  <li>Customise the 404.md page in the root directory</li>
  <li>Enlighten the masses!</li>
</ol>

